    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Validation results demonstrate pressure head MAPE of 4.2% (criterion: <10%) and RH < 1.0 for all operating points. The mesh independence study confirms discretization error is controlled. The CFD model is assessed as credible for the intended COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
